Company Description


MasteryConnect, Inc. operates an educational cloud-based software platform for teachers. The company was founded by Trenton Goble, Michael A. Hewitt, and Douglas Weber in 2009 and is headquartered in Salt Lake City, UT.




Website


http://www.masteryconnect.com






